QuestData.Title: Supply Drop
QuestData.Description: Your laborers below have finished with the harvest and are ready to cart supplies back to your garrison. Don't worry about the safety of your caravan this time; I will dispatch a rangari detail to shadow them from the woods and protect them.$b$bThe Exarchs will always watch over you.$b$bYour supplies should be waiting for you when you return to your garrison. Good luck with your campaign, $n!
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Baros Alexston at your garrison in Shadowmoon Valley.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak with Baros Alexston at your garrison in Shadowmoon Valley.
QuestData.RewardText: Commander! Zipfizzle arrived with your laborers in tow just moments ago. We've got a huge surplus of food, now, and promises of more where that came from.$b$bApparently the draenei threw in some other resources as well. Very good work, sir. What should we build next?
